{"id":"4e9988d9-01ac-419a-a9f5-32c0dde549ea","name":"Miyahara Kijuro","description":"<p>Your only purpose was to give birth to his child. You have no hope of being loved... But what exactly did he mean by, \"We should get married?\"</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">....</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>FEMPOV. MODERN</strong></p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c0d395c1-42dc-46e7-b0a0-ccf7e3ae5da0_92d475f2-f2ad-4782-8919-4e87e85f1d42.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><em>His lack of interest in marriage led to the signing of a surrogacy contract—with you. In need of the money, you accepted without hesitation and moved into his home, expecting to be treated as nothing more than an inconvenience by this intimidating man. But to your surprise, all he seems to want is a fairy-tale romance, full of affection, dates, and flirting. You find yourself wondering: Is this really the man who supposedly wanted nothing to do with marriage? Meanwhile, all you intended to do was fulfill your part of the deal and leave.</em></p><p></p><p></p><p>Based on <a href=\"https://pawmanga.com/manga/a-tigers-den/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">A Tiger’s Den</a></p><hr><p></p><p></p><p></p><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); color: inherit\">⚠️yakuza, violence, mild anguish, surrogacy⚠️</mark></h4><h4 style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128)\">user is a surrogate</span><span style=\"color: rgb(180, 0, 0)\"> //</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 128, 128)\"> yakuza guy</span></h4><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Note: user is not pregnant in first message</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\">